meta {
  name: 7 Ask - grounded, cited answer
  type: http
  seq: 7
}

post {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/ask
  body: json
}

headers {
  X-Clinician-Id: {{clinician}}
}

body:json {
  {
    "patient_id": "{{patient}}",
    "question": "What changed in this patient's labs and what should I pay attention to?"
  }
}

docs {
  Run after ingesting documents for the same patient_id (requests 5-6).

  -> 200 with the multi-agent answer: routing[] shows every supervisor
  handoff (intake -> evidence -> answer) with logged reasons; citations[]
  covers patient facts AND guideline evidence; patient_facts vs
  guideline_evidence are separated; each guideline hit carries hybrid-RAG
  provenance (keyword_rank from BM25, dense_rank from embedding cosine,
  fused_score, rerank_score). degraded=false.
}
